Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,(全國集合來的色情原石\N做愛的人才)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-是 -久等了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒事 -今天多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-邊走邊說吧 -好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被人看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-在藏著嗎 -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太暗了 要開燈\N會有點亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話把眼鏡口罩拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,反正等等也要拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不然會有點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-請多指教 -請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有點眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是英美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姓是深田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 你的姓是深田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是做這個的 認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-知道才來的吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是英美 如果沒搞錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,姓是深田的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,深田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-對吧 -什麼深田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼深田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是很火的一個女優
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還有那種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛才喬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是喬裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是深田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,自白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-是 -什麼是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,報名的人沒有拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是是面向素人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-是嗎 -是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,基本沒有女優來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,女優工作都是找經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的和經紀人說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,事務所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒有 -沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便來會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-我沒事 -真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-今天是私下嗎 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你人氣高\N都預約不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒有 -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的顏色你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-紅色的 -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 這個顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,人氣高的就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-這樣啊 -穿這個很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是人氣高的人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得很花哨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,基本都是穿馬甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-求你了 -為什麼求我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這個當然 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不能拒絕人氣女優
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-求你 -等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等會有問題的 這個要播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你說你已經拍了很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就當是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這不行 會被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,會暴露 還有別的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還有別人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼煩惱的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最近有點 不是壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,提前決定好的太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 有很多企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看了你們公司的\N覺得比較自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-這樣 -還只有素人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我喬裝一下應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,會被發現 但是也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼想演的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那也幫了我們忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這個系列每次都會問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是來幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我去問問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-讓我演啊 -我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-這個花了很多錢\N-這套很難找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很謝謝你 懂很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有一種要去打仗的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-很貴的 -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-知道了嗎 -太逗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個胸 準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 都透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-透嗎 -有點透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,透的也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-有的 -有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很少見 做了那麼多年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-這個系列都五百本了\N-這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,三百四百 很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,AV女優是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,具體的在車裡說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我裝作素人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,手怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-已經暴露了\N-編一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,名字改不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-女大學生 -女大學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,改不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 好好乾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 想要自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的喜歡做愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 問錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-問錯了 -問什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我也看了很多女優
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人是為了營業說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺我在問廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,會被人聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚了 -已經天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是這個車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-坐車去嗎 -走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,請上車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 安全帶也在高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-有這種感覺啊 -有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-這種情況是沒有的 -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-很高興\N-因為沒有女優會來募集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒有嗎 -沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們業界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一般都是找經紀人安排工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,討論之後再決定工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一般是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是有公司的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,其實個人說可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 想做才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還有點喬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,戴眼鏡口罩 眼鏡我見過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,戴著眼鏡的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-有的吧 -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那時才知道戴眼鏡很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 工作的戴眼鏡也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到在這裡遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,會暴露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定會暴露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很可疑啊 還這種穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 虧你能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-暴露了嗎 -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-不能拒絕啊\N-拒絕我也不走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要說 -我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不讓我也要跟著
